    h1.
        EMC
    h2.
        Latest: 1.0.0
    p.
        Adds buildings to deconstruct matter into emc. This emc can be reconstructed into matter later.
        
        <br>
        <a href="https://mod.io/g/shapez/m/shapez-industries" target="_blank" title="Shapez Industries" rel="noopener"><img src="https://image.modcdn.io/members/fed9/10146771/profile/si-transparent.png" alt="si transparent" width="288" height="63"></a>
